<p>B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o c&aacute;c t&#7879;p tin &#273;&iacute;nh k&egrave;m n&#7871;u mu&#7889;n, s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7879;p tin li&#7879;t k&ecirc; &#7903; &#273;&acirc;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c khai b&aacute;o trong t&#7879;p c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.</p>
<p><b>L&#432;u &yacute;:</b> t&#7879;p &#273;&iacute;nh k&egrave;m s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i k&egrave;m theo th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p v&#7899;i &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng HTML v&agrave; s&#7869; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p nh&#432; l&agrave; m&#7897;t li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t tr&ecirc;n website n&#7871;u th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng Text</p>
<p>Tr&#432;&#7901;ng m&ocirc; t&#7843; s&#7869; ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&ugrave;ng trong th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng Text</p>
